@nacalai warning, keep the previous versions of the installers for video and audio fx, because the new video fx is broken in obs, so you want to be able to roll back.
With the master build of obs or with an artefact from a recent PR, video fx works again because i fixed the issue.
You'll want to unzip the artifact in a temp folder and not in Program Files of course or you'll break current obs install.
